RejuvFR is a fan translation mod for Pokémon Rejuvenation.

You are free to use, copy and share it for personal, non commercial purposes.
Please do not resell or repackage it commercially.

Pokémon Rejuvenation is the original creation of Jan and the Rejuvenation team.
All Pokémon names, characters and related assets are trademarks of Nintendo,
Game Freak and The Pokémon Company. This mod is a non profit fan translation
and is not affiliated with, endorsed by or licensed by any of them.

The translation content in this repository is provided as is, without warranty
of any kind. Use at your own discretion.
